{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/handle-click-events-with-javascript-using-the-onclick-property","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"json-apis-and-ajax","demoType":null,"title":"Obradi klik događaje korišćenjem JavaScript-a koristeći atribut `onclick`","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Želite da se vaš kod izvrši čim stranica završi učitavanje. Za tu svrhu, možete priložiti događaj (event) <code>JavaScript</code> na dokument nazvan <code>DOMContentLoaded</code>. Ovo je kod koji to radi:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {});\n</code></pre>\n<p>Možete implementirati rukovaoce događajima koji ulaze u funkciju <code>DOMContentLoaded</code>. Možete implementirati rukovaoc događaja za <code>onclick</code> koji se aktivira kada korisnik klikne na element <code>#getMessage</code>, dodavanjem sledećeg koda:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">document.getElementById('getMessage').onclick = function () {};\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"587d7fad367417b2b2512be1","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodaj rukovaoca događaja klika unutar funkcije za <code>DOMContentLoaded</code> za element sa ID-om <code>getMessage</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"data-visualization","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301503,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/handle-click-events-with-javascript-using-the-onclick-property"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\r\n    // Add your code below this line\r\n    // Add your code above this line\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  body {\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;\r\n  }\r\n  h1 {\r\n    font-size: 2em;\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n  }\r\n  .box {\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    background-color: #eee;\r\n    padding: 20px 5px;\r\n  }\r\n  button {\r\n    color: white;\r\n    background-color: #4791d0;\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    border: 1px solid #4791d0;\r\n    padding: 5px 10px 8px 10px;\r\n  }\r\n  button:hover {\r\n    background-color: #0f5897;\r\n    border: 1px solid #0f5897;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n<h1>Cat Photo Finder</h1>\r\n<p class=\"message box\">The message will go here</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  <button id=\"getMessage\">Get Message</button>\r\n</p>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod bi trebalo da koristi metodu <code>document.getElementById</code> za odabir elementa sa ID-om <code>getMessage</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /document\\s*\\.getElementById\\(\\s*('|\")getMessage\\1\\s*\\)/g);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da doda rukovaoca događaja za <code>onclick</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(document.getElementById('getMessage').onclick);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/data-visualization/#json-apis-and-ajax","dashedName":"handle-click-events-with-javascript-using-the-onclick-property","certification":"data-visualization","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"data-visualization","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"json-apis-and-ajax","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/change-text-with-click-events","prevChallengePa